---
import Layout from '../components/Layout.astro';
import EvolutionSpine from '../components/v22/EvolutionSpine.astro';
import { education,certifications } from '../data/experience';
import { profile } from '../data/profile';
import { absoluteUrl } from '../config/site';
const profilePageJsonLd={ '@context':'https://schema.org','@type':'ProfilePage',name:`About ${profile.name}`,url:absoluteUrl('/about/',true),mainEntity:{'@type':'Person',name:profile.name,jobTitle:profile.role,url:absoluteUrl('/',true),sameAs:[profile.github,profile.linkedin]} };
---
<Layout title="About — Shailesh Dudala" description="The human and technical path from biomedical informatics to predictive healthcare, products, context-engineered agents, and execution harnesses." canonicalPath="/about/" jsonLd={profilePageJsonLd}>
  <section class="about-v22-hero"><div class="shell"><span>ABOUT / HUMAN ORIGIN</span><h1>Ambiguity is where the work begins.</h1><div><p>I started in biomedical informatics, where a technically correct result could still fail if lineage, assumptions, or clinical context were invisible.</p><p>That discipline became a way of working: learn the domain, find the missing abstraction, make uncertainty explicit, and move from prototype to an operating system people can trust.</p></div></div></section>
  <section class="v22-scene"><div class="shell scene-heading"><div><span>THE THROUGHLINE</span><h2>The scope widened. The responsibility did too.</h2></div><p>Clinical data became predictive systems, healthcare products, local document intelligence, bounded agents, and the harness around long-running work.</p></div><div class="shell"><EvolutionSpine compact/></div></section>
  <section class="v22-scene curiosity-field"><div class="shell"><div><span>CURIOSITY / NOT CATEGORY BLUR</span><h2>Different domains expose different failure modes.</h2><p>Healthcare tests lineage, interoperability, and consequential decisions. Insurance tests document ambiguity and workflow authority. Quant and sports forecasting test calibration and backtests. Model behavior tests causal restraint. Coding agents test scope, state, and proof.</p></div><div>{['Learn the domain','Frame the operating decision','Find the missing abstraction','Build the smallest truthful system','Measure failure before scale','Keep people in authority'].map((step,i)=><article><span>{String(i+1).padStart(2,'0')}</span><strong>{step}</strong></article>)}</div></div></section>
  <section class="v22-scene credentials-v22"><div class="shell"><div><span>EDUCATION</span><ul>{education.map((entry)=><li>{entry}</li>)}</ul></div><div><span>CREDENTIALS</span><ul>{certifications.map((entry)=><li>{entry}</li>)}</ul></div></div></section>
</Layout>
